-- About $82 billion left Spain in March: Central bank
-- 
-- Thu May 31, 2012 7:02am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/05/31/us-spain-capital-idUSBRE84U0IU20120531

 

 MADRID  (Reuters) - A total of 66.2 billion euros ($82 billion) of capital, excluding the central bank's operations, left Spain in March, Bank of Spain data showed on Thursday, compared to a entry of 5.4 billion euros in the same month one year ago. 
 (Reporting By Sonya Dowsett; Editing by Sarah White)